Class Eval<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • drjoliv.fjava.adt.Eval<A>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Applicative<Eval.μ,A>, Functor<Eval.μ,A>, Monad<Eval.μ,A>

    public abstract class Eval<A>
extends Object
implements Monad<Eval.μ,A>
    Delays the evaluation of an expression, caching the value the first time the expression is evaluated.
    Author:
    Desonte 'drjoliv' Jolivet : drjoliv@gmail.com
